text: "Unwritten" is a 2004 single by singer Natasha Bedingfield, although the song was not released in the United States until 2006. The song is from her debut record, also titled Unwritten. This song hit number five on the Billboard Hot 100 and became Bedingfield's first top ten hit single in the United States. This single and "Pocketful of Sunshine" are among Bedingfield's most successful singles. It is in the key of B-flat major (in the F Mixolydian mode).
